##China Inflation Period 1948-1949, Air Letters

In 1948 the DGP introduced domestic and foreign formular air letter sheets. The domestic air letter was first issued on 1 Aug 1948, at a fixed price of $120,000 and could be used any time prior to Aug , 1949, without the payment of additional postage, irrespective of future rate increases. 
